{"tid":1002831,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] Enjoy單身！唐詩詠爆料：爸爸驚我嫁唔出","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T11:41:29.000Z","uid":82917,"like":45,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c954beee5e430ff61fb1e735aed5d9021065f7de","tid":1002831,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">知 你 好 撚 恨 嫁 啦<br />\n講 完 未 呀 老 女 人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n藝人唐詩詠出席國際車展，自言由細就好鍾意賽車的快速感，故18歲就即時去考車牌，更一Take Pass：「除咗有學揸私家車，都有學揸電單車，但畀媽咪知道之後就唔畀我再考，話好危險，不過我真係好想喺真正嘅賽車場上面玩。」有同歷任男友玩賽車？她笑言沒有：「但如果將來嘅男友喺呢方面叻都幾吸引，咁有型會加分，同埋如果識埋運動就更加好。（擇偶條件都唔算高？）都仲要睇感覺。」 <br />\n<br />\n曾表示正有一名圈外男士追求的她，被問到「一男子」是否都好賽車？詩詠回避表示：「咁耐以來都冇識一個男仔鍾意。」新年期間驚親友催拍拖？她以肯定語氣回答：「從來都冇，因為有好多親戚都喺台灣、美國。（新年冇假放？）有3日陪爸爸。（爸爸唔會催？）佢唔敢催我，問都唔敢問。」<span style=\"color: red;\">續大爆爸爸曾擔心過自己會嫁唔出</span>：「不過都係唔會問我，收收埋埋咁，都係哥哥話番畀我聽。（會加快步伐快啲識？）咁又唔會，我叫咗爸爸唔好咁擔心。」又笑指已過了自設的結婚歲數界線：「細個想30歲前結婚，但依家都好享受單身，試多啲未做過嘅事。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4A9dWF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4A9dWF.png&h=229d230d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n折撚墮，家陣無契哥哥肯俾佢擺上台煲新聞，陰公到要擺埋老豆上台，仲要話俾全世界知連自己老豆都睇死你賣剩蔗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁蠢既閪。。。閪女人難怪捧極唔紅啦！"},{"pid":"91de99c6120a48e0c2fbc1d6f3f922cf6477a15d","tid":1002831,"uid":94828,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"Uncle應該仲有排驚"},{"pid":"ef2182dda3e0e04def07b58b4d836ad5dd0a07ba","tid":1002831,"uid":152262,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"唐姨醒目 知道單身好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe108cd6513370581f21f2b73aec6ab4d0311657","tid":1002831,"uid":53694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:25:11.000Z","msg":"恨嫁到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173bcdb9e0ac7249cdcb2fde8d2c46908c444cd1","tid":1002831,"uid":223934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"條女很清楚收兵好過嫁人"},{"pid":"592e44f116210c88bbbeb5d5bca0864d095e0734","tid":1002831,"uid":42735,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:26:36.000Z","msg":"睇怕uncle要驚到入棺材<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedcee5fcfa63d6f77f040786abc1a2a2d47eb80","tid":1002831,"uid":90496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"Pretty in my own way.....收皮啦唐姨"},{"pid":"f433f632c61af61afff1c0067791874e6ed806c8","tid":1002831,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0644d03dbcedcbf246ab43e4aaccecd4db818916","tid":1002831,"uid":38526,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"張圖個西字好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fbc983a0205651162ecd6db507e182a24d6797b","tid":1002831,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:31:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f91288fc84318b429e1e314c4750120fd0a76415","tid":1002831,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"洪仔點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611ed53f6b4ccc180b389c23d4fd5522c3aa41e6","tid":1002831,"uid":141396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"（37歲）"},{"pid":"05fc9aedb39dff72d417